                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">Shows that these ancient teachings are penetrating and relevant, not only for understanding death, but as a guide to life. Illustrated.<br><br><br><i>From the Trade Paperback edition.</i></span>
              
